This file marks the Lunette starter TEMPLATE itself.

`create-lunette` deletes it when scaffolding a new project, so its presence tells
you (human or agent) which mode you are in:

- present → you are working ON the template. ADRs may be consolidated / renumbered
  freely (see docs/adr/0001-recording-decisions.md).
- absent  → you are in a project scaffolded FROM the template. ADRs are
  append-only and immutable in meaning; change a decision by writing a new ADR
  that supersedes the old one.

Do not remove this file by hand in the template.
